{"id": 223692898, "title": "APC Will Take Over S\u2019East If I Become Governor \u2013 Chukwuma", "text": "A former national auditor of the All Progressives Congress (APC), Chief Chukwuma Soludo has vowed that the entire South East states will come under the party\u2019s control if he becomes governor of Anambra State. He also promised that the party\u2019s victory in the coming 2025 Anambra State governorship election would be a strong spring board for the party to take over the entire South East region in future elections. As part of his plans to reposition the party for the victory, he said he has hired and donated buildings for the APC state local government secretariat in the 21 LGAs, three senatorial zones and 326 wards in Anambra State. He handed over the keys to the party\u2019s offices to members of the State Working Committee of the party led by the chairman, Chief Basil Ejidike at a ceremony attended in his Umueri, Anambra East local government country home was also attended by many other stakeholders of the party including former members of the House Representatives, Hons Ralph Okeke, Chinedu Eluomuno, Ifeanyi Ibezi, as well as Chief Chidi Orji and Barr C. J. Chinwuba. Sir Chukwuma who is an aspirant of the APC governorship for the Anambra governorship poll promised that he would henceforth fund regular seminars and interactive meetings among members of the party\u2019s leadership at all levels in the state to enable them articulate effective and efficient mobilisation of support strategies from the grassroots ahead of the governorship election.", "summary": "A former national auditor of the All Progressives Congress (APC), Chief Chukwuma Soludo has vowed that the entire South East states will come under the party\u2019s control if he becomes governor of Anambra State. He also promised that the party\u2019s victory in the coming 2025 Anambra State governorship election would be a strong spring board [&#8230;]", "url": "https://leadership.ng/apc-will-take-over-seast-if-i-become-governor-chukwuma/", "image": "https://leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Charles-Soludo.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-26 13:13:29", "author": "Okechukwu Obeta", "authors": ["Okechukwu Obeta"], "language": "en", "source_country": "ng", "sentiment": 0.165}